description:
Proper Japanese Title: ! , !! (Ketchaku no Toki! Sani, Saigo no Chikara!!)

Sunnys bloody battle with Tommyrod reaches its horrific end, and Brunch finds himself locked in an electrifying battle with an immortal warrior that cannot be destroyed!
name: The End Is Here! Sunny's Final Power!

description: A team of scientists and army personal travel across the stars to reach the lost city of Atlantis. This first episode was shown as a double length feature.
name: Rising, Part I & 2

description:
The team are discovering more Ancient artifacts and Rodney finds a device that makes him impenetrable. Problem is that that also means he can't take in any food or drink.

Atlantis experiences power fluctuations and one of the Anthosians reports seeing a shadow in the hallways of Atlantis.
name: Hide and Seek

description: A wraith like bug attacks and bites Sheppard. The team try to rush him back to Atlantis but the Puddle jumper get's stuck in the Stargate. They have only 38 minutes to find a solution and get trough the Stargate before it closes on the puddle jumper and kills them all.
name: Thirty Eight Minutes

description:
The Wraith seem to be at every location the Atlantis away team explores. After one particular harrowing escape Dr. Weir has had enough and suspects a Wraith collaborator. Sgt. Bates immediately suspects one of the Athosians and confines them to quarters while interrogating them one by one.

Halling and other Athosians consider leaving because of the treatment they've received.
name: Suspicion

description: The Atlantis Away Team stumbles on a tribe of young children. The children have a ritual where they kill themselves when they reach their 25th birthday. They think it keeps the Wraith from culling their planet. Rodney thinks there's a ZPM on the planet and wants to take it.
name: Childhood's End

description: Atlantis, with Dr. Carson Beckett, offer to help the Hoffans. They are looking for a way to make themselves, and possibly others, undigestable for the Wraith in the hope that they'll be left alone when the next culling comes. They succeed in making a drug, but the price is very high.
name: Poisoning the Well

description: The Atlantis Away Team, trough Teyla, make contact with a people known as the Genii in the hope that they can trade food with them. They appear to be a simple people who live off the land. To the Wraith it looks as if the civilization isn't big enough to cull, but most Genii live underground. They're making an atom bomb in the hope that they can defeat the Wraith with them.
name: Underground

description: The team arrives on a planet with a heavy fog. The fog is generating a massive amount of energy, allowing travel back to Earth. Once they've arrived on earth they're not allowed to travel back to Atlantis. Things just don't add up.
name: Home

description: Two hurricanes approach Atlantis and because they have no working ZPM to create a protective shield evacuation is necessary. The leader of the people on the planet they evacuate to tell the Genii that Atlantis is going to be empty and defenseless.
name: The Storm

description: Atlanis has been invaded by Commander Acastus Kolya and a team of Genii. The hurricanes are still heading for Atlantis and Dr. Rodney McKay and Elizabeth Weir start repairing the grounding station, while John Sheppard fights Kolya by taking out his men one by one.
name: The Eye

description: John Sheppard, Dr. Rodney McKay and two scientists fly out in the puddle jumper to a Lagrangian point satellite that was once used by the Ancients against the Wraith. Not long after they get there they detect a Wraith distress call from a nearby planet.
name: The Defiant One

description: A team of scientists and military personal are inspecting a section of Atlantis that had been flooded by the recent storm when they contract some kind of virus. The whole city shuts down as Atlantis quarantines itself not allowing any movement between the different sections.
name: Hot Zone

description: The Atlantis Away Team are attacked by a Wraith Darth and try to seek shelter behind a planet when the planet seems to attack and destroy the Wraith ship. The team lands on the pristine planet, even though there's no technology the people claim they've never seen or even heard of the Wraith.
name: Sanctuary

description: The Atlantis team is inspecting an unexplored section of the city and discover a strange room with a stasis pod. The pod contains a very old looking woman holding a piece of paper with gate addresses. The woman is revived and she knows everything about everyone on the mission. The woman turns out to be Weir. She tells her story of their arrival on Atlantis.
name: Before I Sleep

description: One of the gate addresses the old Elizabeth Weir gave them leads them to Dagan where a secret Brotherhood were given a Zero Point Module, which they know as 'Potentia'. They were meant to keep it safe until the descendants of the Ancients return, but because of the Wraith cullings the information on where the ZPM has been stored has been lost. The Atlantis Team will need to solve the puzzle to get at the big prize.
name: The Brotherhood

description: Teyla and John Sheppard are following the Hive ships that are heading for Atlantis. In a desperate effort Dr. Rodney McKay has an idea. He thinks he's able to keep the Stargate to Earth open for 1,3 seconds. Long enough for a data transfer and personal video messages for Earth. Aiden Ford takes it upon himself to record the messages. Meanwhile Teyla and Sheppard are witnessing a massive culling and are powerless to stop the Wraith.
name: Letters from Pegasus

description: As the Hive Ships draw nearer Teyla keeps having nightmares, an old Athosian woman tells her about her abilities to sense the Wraith. The rest of the team are looking for anything and everything to get ready for the arrival of the Hive Ships.
name: The Gift

description: Teyla finds out the Wraith armada will pass the Ancient weapons platform on their way to Atlantis and Dr. Rodney McKay and Dr. Radek Zelenka think they can get it repaired in time for the Wraith's pass. Teyla and Sargent Bates get into a heated argument, Bates is found beaten up later.
name: The Siege: Part I

description: The Atlantis Team sets the self destruct in wait for the approaching Hive Ships and a full evacuation is ordered when Colonel Everett arrives with reinforcements, promising even more in four days. He relieves Elizabeth Weir of her post and takes command, he's angry at John Sheppard for what he did to Colonel Marshall Sumner and they get off on the wrong foot. Atlantis is made ready for the imminent attack, battle stations are manned as the Wraith start their attack.
name: The Siege, Part II

description: The city of Atlantis is slowly falling in the hands of the Wraith. Sheppard has a Genii A-bomb that he wants to use to blow up a Wraith Hive Ship. The Deadalus arrives just in time to help, but the battle seems lost. Another twelve Hive Ships are on their way.
name: The Siege, Part III

description: A few months after the siege of Atlantis a couple of members of the Atlantis team are returning to Atlantis on the Deadalus. The trip takes eighteen days and they're pretty boring until Dr. Rodney McKay finds a Wraith computer virus, which is transmitting their position to the Wraith, on the Deadalus' computers.
name: The Intruder

description: The Atlantis Team track Aiden Ford to a planet and go to investigate. Major Lorne and McKay are taken hostage by Ford as he explains to McKay that he's just fine with his addiction and even thinks it's the way to ultimately defeat the Wraith.
name: Runner

description: When investigating a planet the Atlantis Team is surprised by a Wraith Dart. McKay and Laura Cadman are scooped up into the memory bank of the Dart before it's shot down. The power levels of the Dart are low and they are only able to pull McKay out, the problem is that he shares his brain with Laura Cadman.
name: Duet

description: Neither Teyla nor Ronon Dex have ever visited the planet the Puddle jumper lands on. They're attacked by the indigenous people, and subsequently rescued by the Olesians. Their magistrate wants to trade with the Atlantis team and the puddle jumper returns for Elizabeth Weir
name: Condemned

description: Dr. Rodney McKay finds an abandoned Ancient project. They were trying to build a new power source but never got to finish it. McKay is confident he can finish the job the Ancients started. Meanwhile Ronon Dex finds out he's not the only survivor of his home world.
name: Trinity

description: The Atlantis Team arrive on a planet where an old man is taking care of a young wraith girl. He's giving here a herbal serum to control her hunger. Dr. Carson Beckett is actively making a retrovirus to turn Wraith into humans.
name: Instinct

description: Sheppard has been bitten by the wraith girl Ellia, infected with the retrovirus and he's rushed to the infirmary only to find that his injury has healed itself. He starts to transform into a Iratus Bug and needs stem cells from one of the creatures eggs. But is Sheppard too far along to care?
name: Conversion

description: Dr. Rodney McKay finds the long range scanners and activates them. It shows the Ancients ship the Aurora and they send out the Deadalus to investigate. The Aurora is heavily damaged and the crew is, and has been, in stasis for 10.000 years. They are connected trough a virtual reality network, John Sheppard logs himself onto the network to warn the Ancients of the wraith that are closing in on their position.
name: Aurora

description: Aiden Ford and his band of Wraith enzyme taking outlaws capture the Atlantis Away Team and forces McKay, Teyla and Ronon to take the enzyme so they can go on a mission together.
name: The Lost Boys

description: After Aiden Ford's plan fails miserably the team are captured by the Wraith and interrogated. They try to escape from their cell when Teyla senses the approach of another Hive Ship. It seems there is some animosity between the two Wraith teams. Dr. McKay takes more of the enzyme to try and get back to Atlantis and warn them.
name: The Hive

description: The Atlantis team find a cave that has a window to another world. Sheppard gets pulled in and McKay finds out that time moves a lot faster on the other side. Sheppard gets tired of waiting and explores the other world.
name: Epiphany

description: The Goa'uld have a mole on Atlantis and have planted a bomb, it's up to the Deadalus to warn the Atlantis team to not open the gate to Earth becasue that will trigger the explosion.
name: Critical Mass

description: McKay is trapped in a puddle jumper on the bottom of the ocean of the planet where Atlantis is located. He starts having hallucinations.
name: Grace Under Pressure

description: The Atlantis Team find a world where the inhabitants can protect themselves from the Wraith with Ancient technology.
name: The Tower

description: The team discover two life pods floating in space, one with a man and one with a woman. When they open the pod that holds the woman Weir gets imprinted with the mind of the woman. She has a special favor to ask.
name: The Long Goobye

description: The death of Major Evan Lorne shocks all at Atlantis and Ronon Dex and Teyla are sent out to find out what happened. Atlantis gets a call from Ladon Radim who's got a ZPM to offer them in trade.
name: Coup D'etat

description: Michael Kenmore awakes in the infirmary not able to remember what happened to him. The only words that have any meaning to him are Wraith and Atlantis. He tries to go about his daily business, but finds that people act strangely around him. He goes in search of information about himself.
name: Michael

description: The cloaked city of Atlantis is awaiting the arrival of the Hive ship. The Wraith sends an audio signal. Turns out it's Michael the Wraith/Human hybrid. He asks for help as fighting has broken out among the different Wraith clans over the short supplies of food.
name: Allies

description: Dr. Rodney McKay and Ronon Dex have stayed behind on the Wraith Hive ship trying to implement the retrovirus but they're betrayed by the Wraith. Sheppard takes an X-302 and tries to free his team members. He get's help from an unexpected source.
name: No Man's Land

description: The severely damaged Deadalus has minimal life-support capabilities and the decision is made to transport all non-essential personnel to the Wraith Hive ship after deployment of the retrovirus was a success.
name: Misbegotten

description: The Atlantis team are looking for Stargates to make the Galactic Bridge to Earth. They land on a planet and a come in contact with a man called Lucius Lavin. Dr. Beckett is immediately smitten with him and tells him all about the city of Atlantis. The man is adored by the whole town and part of the away team, except for Sheppard who seems immune.
name: Irresistible

description: Ronon is once again captured by the Wraith and made a Runner again. They take him to his home world and hunt him down, but this time the Atlantis Team are on his trail as well.
name: Sateda

description: The Atlantis team are contacted by, what they perceive to be, the ancients. The team sets out to meet them and even Elizabeth Weir joins the team. They find a very large city that is powered by an unlimited number of ZPM's. Elizabeth tries to discuss a trade but Oberoth - their leader, is not interested. The team gets a feeling that something isn't right.
name: Progeny

description: Elizabeth Weir wakes up in a mental hospital on Earth where she's told the Atlantis expedition was a fabrication of her mind. She's let out of the hospital and goes on with her life, but something's troubling her.
name: Real World

description: The renegade Commander Acastus Kolya takes John Sheppard prisoner and puts him in a cell next to a Wraith. He wants to trade Sheppard for Ladon Radim and tortures Sheppard to show Elizabeth Weir the level of his resolve. John Sheppard and the Wraith start working together to try to escape while the Atlantis team is frantically looking for the planet where Kolya keeps them captive.
name: Common Ground

description: Jeannie Miller - Rodney's sister, solves a mathematical proof that may provide means for transferring particles to a parallel universe. Rodney is sent to earth to get her to come to Atlantis so they can work on the problem together. The brother and sister are socially very different creatures and everyone quickly warms to Jeannie and her stories of a young Rodney, to the dismay of her brother.
name: McKay and Mrs. Miller

description: Major Sheppard's team go in search of the Atlantis team led by Major Leonard. They find team members dead, they've been killed by Leonard and they're now also under attack from him. The planet makes everyone hallucinate to the point where they murder each other thinking they are someone else. Ronon and Sheppard are locked in battle while Rodney tries to find out how the Wraith machine works so he can turn it off.
name: Phantoms

description: Earth and Atlantis are finally ready to start their first test with the interstellar subway that will link Earth to Atlantis. The first trip goes off without a hitch although McKay does spot an anomaly. It turns out to be an Ancient ship traveling just below the speed of light because they've lost their hyper-drive. The Daedalus assists in repairing the hyper drive and when they get to Atlantis the Ancients immediately take it back into their own hands.
name: The Return, Part I

description: Atlantis is under attack by the Replicators and the Ancients have lost. General O'Neill and Richard Woolsey are the only two persons still alive on Atlantis and the General has orders to destroy the city if it falls into enemy hands. McKay has a plan to destroy the Replicators but he must do so before they are able to reprogram themselves.
name: The Return, Part II
